","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35879,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/parable-baqarah-ali-imran\/","url_meta":{"origin":3920,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Parable of Surat al-Baqarah and Ali \u2018Imran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLearn Surat al-Baqarah, for adhering to it is blessed, leaving it is sorrow, and the sorcerers cannot defeat it. Learn al-Baqarah and Ali \u2018Imran, for they are both the brightly illuminated chapters coming on the Day of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35550,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/05\/ism-al-atham\/","url_meta":{"origin":3920,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Greatest name of Allah in these two verses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 5, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Asma\u2019 bint Yazid reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe greatest name of Allah is in these two verses: Your God is one God, there is no God but Him, the Gracious, the Merciful (2:163). As well as the opening of Surat Ali \u2018Imran: Allah, there\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/last-ayat-surah-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3920,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Last two verses of al-Baqarah sufficient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites the last two verses of Surat al-Baqarah in the night, it is enough for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 807 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/ali-three-baqarah-before-bed\/","url_meta":{"origin":3920,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Quran: Recite last three verses of al-Baqarah before bed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI have not seen anyone of intelligence go to sleep until he had recited these three verses at the end of Surat al-Baqarah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 3289 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0642 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0651\u064d \u0631\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3876,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/28\/shaytan-runs-surah-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3920,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Satan runs from Al-Baqarah recitation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not turn your houses into graveyards. Verily, Satan flees from the house in which Surat al-Baqarah is recited.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 780 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3920","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\